The "ONeillo v1.0" application was developed by Dr Peter O'Neill of Sheffield Hallam University, for his level 4 Students on the module, "Programming for Computing."
This "ONeillo v1.0" application uses most, if not all of the techniques explained and demonstrated throughout the year. (The GUllmageArray used within the application was provided to the Students.
